{"tid":1160971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男性侵80歲阿嬤　「身體原因」未得逞落跑","createTime":"2019-05-18T22:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T04:42:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29c4e53653d9133348ce7c5078f8d94395d94493","tid":1160971,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T22:14:31.000Z","msg":"中國一名男子性侵80歲阿嬤，因「身體原因」未得逞，逃離現場後被逮，判有期徒刑兩年十個月。<br />\n據《人民法院報》報導，5月13日，中國四川屏山縣人民法院審理一起強姦未遂案，案件指出，36歲王男，在2017年9月7日騎車時，遇到80歲阿嬤金翠花，王男就以想要看桂圓為由，叫阿嬤上車到她房子內，得知阿嬤家只有一人，於是王男欲與阿嬤發生性關係被拒，於是強壓阿嬤在床上，並用自己的身體以及手臂壓住阿嬤強行進行性行為，不過因身體原因未得逞而逃離現場。<br />\n而王男在2018年7月11日14時，騎摩托車遇道另一名50歲女子柳英，抓住她想跟她發生性關係時，因有人路過，王男未得逞逃離現場。法院指出，王男兩次用暴力手段，想跟二女發生性關係而未得逞，判有期徒刑兩年十個月。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190519/640_204b9cb06eff870e6001a5e0151f4a60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190519%2F640_204b9cb06eff870e6001a5e0151f4a60.jpg&h=b0dafa88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190519/640_5e82698f9790adb04cad0af5a8a60a10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190519%2F640_5e82698f9790adb04cad0af5a8a60a10.jpg&h=cee8095f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190519/1569215/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190519%2F1569215%2F&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=5f09c4d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190519%2F1569215%2F&h=feb06bae\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190519/1569215/</a>"},{"pid":"f691f38421f4b065bbc9d1d12a3cf2b0a2d504de","tid":1160971,"uid":90820,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T22:16:13.000Z","